{
  "stem": "19550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Philip E.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Katz, P-H-L-I-- P-H-I-L-I-P E K-A-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ephraim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "E-P-H-R-A-I-M.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name was Fulop, F-U umlaut L-O umlaut P.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Katz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually I shouldn't say that because there was a period of time in the United States when for a funny reason I was known as Mr.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Philip because there was another man by the name of Franz Joseph Katz in the same office that I was at who preceded me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so it was decided to avoid confusion that I would be called Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ephraim Philip until the man, Franz Joseph Katz, was transferred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I could recover my name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was known as Fulop Katz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And familiarly with most people in my town, known as [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fischu, ?] which was very kind of a distortion of my Yiddish name, which was [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fischel. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March 1, 1924.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Kisvarda, K-I-S-V-A-R-D-A, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, for Hungary, a medium-sized town of about 18,000 to 20,000, and served as an administrative and market center in the county of Sabolcs, S-A-B-A-- B-O, I'm sorry, B-O-L-C-S.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 7 hyphen 9 Saint Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's L-A-S-Z-L-O-A-- L-O, I'm sorry, Street, which was the main street in Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- our home was located virtually dead center in the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's easier said than done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kisvarda, as I said had, about 18,000 to 20,000 population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish population constituted almost one third of the population of, of the town.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
